---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="母亲节快乐 ❤️" description="献给世界上最伟大的人——母亲">
  <div class="mother-page">
    <!-- 花瓣飘落 -->
    <div class="petals" aria-hidden="true">
      <span class="petal p1">🌸</span>
      <span class="petal p2">🌷</span>
      <span class="petal p3">💐</span>
      <span class="petal p4">🌺</span>
      <span class="petal p5">🌸</span>
      <span class="petal p6">🌷</span>
      <span class="petal p7">💮</span>
      <span class="petal p8">🌼</span>
      <span class="petal p9">🌸</span>
      <span class="petal p10">🌺</span>
    </div>

    <!-- 顶部装饰波纹 -->
    <div class="top-wave" aria-hidden="true">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 1440 120" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <path d="M0 60C240 20 480 100 720 60C960 20 1200 100 1440 60V0H0V60Z" fill="rgba(232,160,180,0.12)"/>
        <path d="M0 80C240 40 480 120 720 80C960 40 1200 120 1440 80V0H0V80Z" fill="rgba(232,160,180,0.08)"/>
      </svg>
    </div>

    <!-- 主视觉区 -->
    <section class="hero-mother">
      <div class="hero-badge">
        <span class="badge-icon">🌷</span>
        <span>2026 年 5 月 10 日 · 母亲节</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="hero-heading">
        献给世界上<br />
        <span class="highlight">最伟大的人</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-desc">
        她用一生诠释了什么是无私的爱。<br />
        今天，我想把所有的温柔都献给她。
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- 祝福卡片 -->
    <section class="message-section">
      <div class="card main-card">
        <div class="card-inner">
          <div class="card-icon">💝</div>
          <h2>妈妈，母亲节快乐</h2>
          <p>
            感谢您把最好的年华给了我，<br />
            感谢您在我跌倒时扶我起来，<br />
            感谢您教会我善良与坚强。
          </p>
          <p>
            您的笑容是我世界里最温暖的光。<br />
            愿岁月温柔待您，<br />
            愿您永远健康、快乐、美丽。
          </p>
          <p class="card-signature">
            永远爱您的孩子：金恩泽 ❤️
          </p>
          <div class="card-divider"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="cards-grid">
        <div class="card small-card" style="--card-delay: 0.1s">
          <div class="card-inner">
            <span class="small-card-icon">🌷</span>
            <h3>感恩</h3>
            <p>感谢妈妈无条件的爱与付出，是您让我成为今天的自己。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card small-card" style="--card-delay: 0.2s">
          <div class="card-inner">
            <span class="small-card-icon">💪</span>
            <h3>力量</h3>
            <p>您是我人生中最坚强的后盾，给我面对一切的勇气。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card small-card" style="--card-delay: 0.3s">
          <div class="card-inner">
            <span class="small-card-icon">✨</span>
            <h3>祝福</h3>
            <p>愿时光慢一些，愿您的每一天都充满欢笑与温暖。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 引用区 -->
    <section class="quote-section">
      <blockquote>
        <p>"母亲，是第一个爱你的人，也是第一个你爱的人。"</p>
      </blockquote>
    </section>

    <!-- 底部提示 -->
    <section class="cta-section">
      <p class="cta-text">今天，别忘了给妈妈打个电话，说一声</p>
      <p class="cta-big">"妈妈，我爱你 ❤️"</p>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>


<style>
  /* ===== 浅色主题全局覆盖 ===== */
  :global(:root) {
    --color-bg: #fef9f5;
    --color-bg-elevated: #ffffff;
    --color-text: #3d2e2a;
    --color-text-muted: #8c7a72;
    --color-border: #f0e4dc;
    --mother-pink: #d4788f;
    --mother-rose: #c06078;
    --mother-gold: #c8966e;
    --mother-blush: #fce4ec;
  }

  :global(html) {
    background: #fef9f5;
    color: #3d2e2a;
  }

  :global(body) {
    background: #fef9f5;
    color: #3d2e2a;
  }

  :global(.noise-overlay) {
    opacity: 0.015;
  }

  :global(.grain-overlay) {
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 20% 0%, rgba(212, 120, 143, 0.08) 0%, transparent 50%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 80% 100%, rgba(200, 150, 110, 0.05) 0%, transparent 50%);
  }

  :global(header) {
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #fef9f5 60%, transparent);
  }

  :global(nav a) {
    color: #8c7a72;
  }

  :global(nav a:hover) {
    color: #3d2e2a;
  }

  :global(.header-line) {
    background: linear-gradient(to right, #f0e4dc, transparent 50%);
  }

  :global(footer) {
    border-color: #f0e4dc;
  }

  :global(footer p) {
    color: #8c7a72;
  }

  :global(.logo) {
    color: #3d2e2a;
  }

  :global(main p) {
    color: #3d2e2a;
  }

  /* ===== 顶部装饰波纹 ===== */
  .top-wave {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    z-index: 1;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .top-wave svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
  }

  /* ===== 花瓣飘落动画 ===== */
  .petals {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 1;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .petal {
    position: absolute;
    top: -60px;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: petalFall linear infinite;
  }

  .p1  { left: 5%;  animation-duration: 12s; animation-delay: 0s;   font-size: 1.3rem; }
  .p2  { left: 15%; animation-duration: 14s; animation-delay: 1.5s; font-size: 1.6rem; }
  .p3  { left: 25%; animation-duration: 11s; animation-delay: 3s;   font-size: 1.1rem; }
  .p4  { left: 35%; animation-duration: 15s; animation-delay: 0.8s; font-size: 1.8rem; }
  .p5  { left: 45%; animation-duration: 13s; animation-delay: 2.2s; font-size: 1.4rem; }
  .p6  { left: 55%; animation-duration: 16s; animation-delay: 4s;   font-size: 1.2rem; }
  .p7  { left: 65%; animation-duration: 10s; animation-delay: 1s;   font-size: 1.5rem; }
  .p8  { left: 75%; animation-duration: 14s; animation-delay: 2.8s; font-size: 1.7rem; }
  .p9  { left: 85%; animation-duration: 12s; animation-delay: 3.5s; font-size: 1.3rem; }
  .p10 { left: 92%; animation-duration: 15s; animation-delay: 0.5s; font-size: 1.6rem; }

  @keyframes petalFall {
    0% {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg) scale(0.6);
    }
    5% {
      opacity: 0.6;
    }
    50% {
      opacity: 0.4;
      transform: translateY(50vh) rotate(180deg) scale(1);
    }
    90% {
      opacity: 0.2;
    }
    100% {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(100vh) rotate(360deg) scale(0.4);
    }
  }

  /* ===== Hero ===== */
  .hero-mother {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem 0 5rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.5rem 1.2rem;
    background: rgba(212, 120, 143, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(212, 120, 143, 0.2);
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--mother-rose);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out;
  }

  .badge-icon {
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .hero-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 8vw, 4.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out 0.15s both;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .highlight {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--mother-pink), var(--mother-rose));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }

  .hero-desc {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 2;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out 0.3s both;
  }

  /* ===== 卡片 ===== */
  .message-section {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    padding: 1rem 0 4rem;
  }

  .card {
    background: #fffdfb;
    border: 1px solid #f0e4dc;
    border-radius: 16px;
    transition: all 0.4s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(180, 140, 120, 0.06);
  }

  .card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(212, 120, 143, 0.25);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(212, 120, 143, 0.1);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .card-inner {
    padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
  }

  .main-card {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out 0.45s both;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .main-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 4px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #f8c8d4, var(--mother-pink), var(--mother-gold));
  }

  .card-icon {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    animation: pulseIcon 3s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .main-card h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--mother-rose), var(--mother-gold));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }

  .main-card h2::before {
    display: none;
  }

  .main-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 2;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .card-signature {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--mother-rose);
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .card-divider {
    width: 60px;
    height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--mother-pink), rgba(212, 120, 143, 0.1));
    margin: 1.5rem auto 0;
    border-radius: 1px;
  }

  .cards-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .small-card {
    text-align: center;
    animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out var(--card-delay) both;
  }

  .small-card .card-inner {
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
  }

  .small-card-icon {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .small-card:hover .small-card-icon {
    transform: scale(1.15);
  }

  .small-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
    color: var(--mother-rose);
  }

  .small-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* ===== 引用 ===== */
  .quote-section {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    padding: 4rem 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .quote-section blockquote {
    border: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .quote-section p {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 3vw, 1.5rem);
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .quote-section p::before {
    content: '"';
    position: absolute;
    left: -1.5rem;
    top: -0.5rem;
    font-size: 3rem;
    color: var(--mother-pink);
    opacity: 0.2;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
  }

  .quote-section p::after {
    content: '"';
    position: absolute;
    right: -1.5rem;
    bottom: -2rem;
    font-size: 3rem;
    color: var(--mother-pink);
    opacity: 0.2;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
  }

  /* ===== CTA ===== */
  .cta-section {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem 0 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid #f0e4dc;
  }

  .cta-text {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease-out both;
  }

  .cta-big {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--mother-pink), var(--mother-rose));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease-out 0.15s both;
  }

  /* ===== 响应式 ===== */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .cards-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .small-card .card-inner {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .hero-mother {
      padding: 2rem 0 3rem;
    }

    .quote-section {
      padding: 2.5rem 0;
    }
  }

  @keyframes pulseIcon {
    0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); }
    50% { transform: scale(1.08); }
  }
</style>
